## Prerequisites

1. **gogcli** must be installed and configured
   ```bash
   brew install steipete/tap/gogcli
   # or build from source
   ```

2. **Authenticate with gogcli**
   ```bash
   gog auth add your@gmail.com
   export GOG_ACCOUNT=your@gmail.com
   ```

## Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone <repo-url>
cd gmail-newsletter-manager

# Install in development mode
pip install -e .

# Or install with dev dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

## Quick Start

```bash
# Discover newsletters in your inbox
newsletter-manager discover

# List all detected newsletters
newsletter-manager list

# Organize newsletters with auto-categorization
newsletter-manager organize --auto-categorize

# Create Gmail filters for auto-labeling
newsletter-manager create-filters

# View engagement report
newsletter-manager report

# Find newsletters you never read
newsletter-manager recommend-unsubscribe

# Cleanup old newsletters
newsletter-manager cleanup --older-than 30d
```

## Usage

### Discovery
```bash
newsletter-manager discover [--days 90] [--min-frequency 2]
newsletter-manager list [--category Tech] [--unread-only]
newsletter-manager stats [--sender sender@example.com]
```

### Organization
```bash
newsletter-manager organize [--dry-run] [--auto-categorize]
newsletter-manager label <sender> <category/subcategory>
newsletter-manager create-filters [--dry-run]
```

### Management
```bash
newsletter-manager cleanup [--older-than 30d] [--unread-only]
newsletter-manager archive <category|sender> [--older-than 7d]
newsletter-manager unsubscribe [--show-links] [--never-read]
newsletter-manager pause <sender|category>
newsletter-manager resume <sender|category>
```

### Analytics
```bash
newsletter-manager report [--period 30d]
newsletter-manager engagement [--min-open-rate 10]
newsletter-manager recommend-unsubscribe
```

### Utilities
```bash
newsletter-manager export [--format csv|json]
newsletter-manager search <query> [--newsletters-only]
newsletter-manager mark-read <category|sender>
newsletter-manager digest [--daily|--weekly]
```

## Configuration

Configuration file: `~/.gmail-newsletter-manager/config.yaml`

```yaml
categories:
  Tech:
    keywords: [programming, developer, tech, software, coding]
    domains: [dev.to, hashnode.com, medium.com]
  Business:
    keywords: [business, entrepreneur, startup, marketing]
  News:
    keywords: [news, daily, briefing, today]

newsletter_patterns:
  - "list-unsubscribe"
  - "newsletter"
  - "digest"
  - "weekly update"
  - "monthly roundup"

known_platforms:
  - substack.com
  - beehiiv.com
  - mailchimp.com
  - constantcontact.com
  - convertkit.com

auto_archive_days: 30
min_frequency_for_newsletter: 2
```

